Exceptional Needs Payments
</title>
    
    <meta name="description" content="Exceptional Needs Payments are paid to people who have essential, once-off and exceptional needs that they cannot meet out of their weekly income. It can be paid for funeral costs and fuel bills. You must have little or no means.">
    
